            "title": "內地A股早市繼續爭持 紫金創新高半日再漲逾4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市今早仍未擺脫爭持局面，金融行業板塊造好，支撐滬市繼續跑贏深市。紫金礦業(02899)A股(0601899.SH)創新高，早市再漲逾4%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"紫金礦業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/02899-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"紫金礦業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/02899-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">紫金礦業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指今早輕微低開，初段跌幅曾擴大至30點，低見4101點，其後逐漸收復失地，於上午10時半過後進入好淡爭持階段，但高位僅見4142點，升9點；滬指中午收報4134點，升1點或0.03%，半日成交降至8209.41億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指今早則幾乎全程報跌，初段高位14329點時僅升12點，中段低位報14105點，挫211點，其後跌勢回順；深指中午收報14262點，跌53點或0.37%，成交1.05萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數則轉升13點或0.3%，收報4720點；創業板指數更漲14點或0.44%，報3333點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國人壽官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20240425_FI_source-web_02628-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國人壽官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20240425_FI_source-web_02628-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國人壽官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金融行業是今早少數報升的板塊，當中以保險股表現領先，中國人壽(02628)A股(601628.SH)漲4.22%，報48.91元；中國太保(02601)A股(601601.SH)升3.23%，報44.74元；中國平安(02318)A股(601318.SH)升3.07%，報66.11元；新華保險(01336)A股(601336.SH)升2.7%，報82.16元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紫金礦業旗下紫金黃金(02259)計畫動用相等於約280億元，收購於多倫多上市的聯合黃金，兩公司H股今早已雙雙再度破頂。紫金礦業A股同樣創新高，最高曾衝上42.68元；中午收報41.35元，仍漲4.68%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15615242-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e7%b9%bc%e7%ba%8c%e7%88%ad%e6%8c%81-%e7%b4%ab%e9%87%91%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%86%8d%e6%bc%b2%e9%80%be4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250409_FI_source-ap_China-2-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-27 11:47:46",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
